title: Beautiful Building!! Studio for rent!
posting_body: ['NEW VACANCY!', 'This is a Beautiful Studio, One Bath apartment for rent with hardwood floors.', 'Between a few miles from USC and blocks away from the 10 freeway entrance.', 'Great Location!', 'Please contact our property manager Flor to schedule a private viewing and/or for more information.', '**Pictures may be of a similar unit.', 'LISTING INFORMATION: STUDIO-1 Bathroom Monthly Rent$1,350 | Security Deposit $1,350 Hardwood floors Utilities Included!', 'No Parking One Year Lease No Pets Laundry on site CURRENT STATUS:', 'New recent vacancy, currently being worked on.', 'Showing "as is".', 'Looking to rent this unit promptly!', "You may apply online at On-Site's link using the property number below:  Thank you for your time and our Team wishes you a great day!", 'FRED LEEDS PROPERTIES Call the leasing team to set up an appointment to view at', 'show contact info', '.']
